    Network
================
#Local port check
netstat -aon #show all ports
netstat -tlpn #show Listening ports with PID
ss
#Remote port check
nc -zv <ip> <port>
telnet <ip> <port>
#Check bandwith
iperf3


    Memory
================
vmstat

     CPU
================
 top
 
    Disk
================
df -h #show disks usage
lsblk #show block devices
iotop #show disk usage real time
iostat <sec> #disk usage real time
lsof #show open files

    System
================
uptime #show load average
